window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The next book in the thrilling <i>New York Times</i> best-selling series.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>For years he has endured the endless trials and triumphs of a man whose skill and power could not be restrained. Battling ancient enemies, forging new alliances, and confronting the corruption within his own land, Gaius Octavian became a legendary man of war - and the rightful First Lord of Alera.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>But now, the savage Vord are on the march, and Gaius must lead his legions to the Calderon Valley to stand against them - using all of his intelligence, ingenuity, and furycraft to save their world from eternal darkness.</p>"; 
